comments.body: Yes. This was originally taken in April 2016, not 2017. I’m thinking now this more resembles a Pine Warbler but honestly still not sure. I had it on e-bird as a Pine Siskin, which seems extremely out of region (GA) for the time of year.  Pretty horrible photo, but wanted to see if this could be identified.
